It's very much possible, I trust you. I am always a bit wary because even though demonic possession is a real phenomenon I think sometimes regular psychiatric diseases without a demonic substrate can imitate it convincingly outwardly.

One time I also saw someone I still think was demonically possessed or was dabbling into some horrible things, was a teenage aged guy walking on the street in broad daylight with an aura of pure malice, very short and not dangerous physically but an aura of pure evil and dread.

I think you have to be careful not to become paranoid especially if it's about stuff like hand signs or gestures, often times it's just people repeating patterns they have seen from culture/media and not something they do consciouly or a sign they are up to anything nefarious.

I see. I guess if they actually spelled it out it might also be possible they are trying to provoke or antagonize you to get a reaction out of you and use it to get you fired, knowing you are wary about occult stuff. In any case I hope you will remain careful and be safe.
